title: Holiday Buffalo Plaid Set of 2 Merry Christmas Gnome Wall Decor Art, Multicolor
features: These gnomes provide a welcome entry with a farmhouse feel.
Perfect wall decor for the home who loves the rustic buffalo plaid pattern gnome.
These gnomes look great on any wall or accent furniture to include the kitchen and bathroom.
These gnomes measure 14 in H x 8 in L x 0.2 in W
Large for Door or front of home display. Wooden and flat for a seamless hanging display.
Two small silver adhesive hooks included holds up to 0.5lbs
Painted design is made of MDF with wood texture on surface, the sign could surely be used for a long time.
Greet your family and friends with this welcome and Merry Christmas display, which is good choice for indoor decor. Come and decorate your home now.
description: Give your home a room update with these Christmas Gnomes art prints. This set of 2 family or living room design prints feature holiday themed gnomes. This two piece set Gnome signs sits on a flat wooden plaque and measures (8"x 14"in) and has been Hand Painted featuring Hand Painted Accenting One black and white buffalo plaid checkered gnome holds a red gift sign that says “ Merry Christmas”. The other gnome is styled in red and black buffalo plaid and holds a green wreath that says “ Welcome”. These are great additions to your seasonal rustic holiday decor to use as you wish. Some great style ideas would be kitchen, living room, front door, or fireplace mantle. The nose and hands separate wood overlays for an attractive Layered-Look. Each plaque has an attached red nylon rope for easy hanging. This set includes 2 adhesive wall hooks for easy display and hanging.
